tickets.title: Payment Gateway Error - Transaction Timeout
tickets.description: Customer experienced a timeout during checkout process while attempting to purchase Premium Business Plan. Payment of $299.99 was debited from their account but order confirmation was not received. Requires immediate investigation and refund processing.

tickets.title: API Rate Limit Exceeded - Third Party Integration
tickets.description: Enterprise client's CRM integration is failing due to API rate limit being exceeded. Their automated workflows are disrupted affecting customer data synchronization. Current limit: 1000 requests/hour, they need 2500 requests/hour.

tickets.title: Database Connection Pool Exhaustion
tickets.description: Customer's application is experiencing intermittent connection failures during peak hours (2-4 PM EST). Error logs show connection pool exhaustion. They're losing approximately $500/hour in revenue during outages.

tickets.title: SSL Certificate Renewal Failed
tickets.description: Customer's website SSL certificate failed to auto-renew causing browser security warnings. Their e-commerce site is now showing 'Not Secure' warnings affecting customer trust and sales conversion rates.

tickets.title: Multi-Factor Authentication Loop Error
tickets.description: Customer is stuck in an infinite MFA verification loop. After entering the correct OTP, the system redirects back to MFA prompt. Unable to access dashboard for 48+ hours. Phone number verified as correct.

tickets.title: Bulk Data Export Memory Overflow
tickets.description: Customer attempting to export 2.5M records encounters memory overflow error. Export process fails at 45% completion. They need this data for quarterly audit compliance by January 31st deadline.

tickets.title: Webhook Delivery Failure - 502 Bad Gateway
tickets.description: Customer's webhook endpoints are receiving 502 Bad Gateway responses for the past 72 hours. Critical order notifications are not being delivered to their inventory management system causing stock discrepancies.

tickets.title: GDPR Data Deletion Request Incomplete
tickets.description: Customer submitted GDPR Article 17 'Right to be Forgotten' request 15 days ago. While main profile was deleted, backup systems and cached data still contain personal information. Legal compliance at risk.

tickets.title: CDN Cache Invalidation Not Working
tickets.description: Customer updated their website content 6 hours ago but changes are not reflecting globally. CDN cache invalidation requests return success but old content persists in 15+ edge locations worldwide.

tickets.title: OAuth 2.0 Scope Permission Escalation
tickets.description: Customer's application is requesting elevated permissions that weren't part of initial OAuth consent. Users are receiving unexpected permission prompts causing 67% drop in successful authentication flows.

tickets.title: Real-time WebSocket Connection Dropping
tickets.description: Customer's real-time trading application experiences WebSocket disconnections every 3-7 minutes. Reconnection attempts succeed but cause data gaps in live market feeds affecting trading decisions.

tickets.title: Elasticsearch Index Corruption Detected
tickets.description: Customer's search functionality returning inconsistent results due to index corruption. Search queries for products containing 'wireless' return 0 results despite 1,247 matching products in the database.

tickets.title: Container Orchestration Resource Limits
tickets.description: Customer's Kubernetes pods are being terminated due to memory limits during traffic spikes. Current allocation: 2GB RAM, actual usage peaks at 3.2GB during promotional campaigns causing service disruptions.

tickets.title: JWT Token Signature Validation Error
tickets.description: Customer's mobile app users experiencing random logout issues. JWT tokens are being rejected with 'invalid signature' errors despite being within expiration time. Affects 23% of iOS users specifically.

tickets.title: SMTP Server Blacklist Detection
tickets.description: Customer's transactional emails (password resets, receipts) are being marked as spam or blocked entirely. IP address 192.168.45.112 appears on multiple blacklists. Email delivery rate dropped to 34%.

tickets.title: Terraform State File Corruption
tickets.description: Customer's infrastructure deployment pipeline failed due to corrupted Terraform state file. Unable to apply changes or rollback. Production environment is stable but no updates can be deployed.

tickets.title: GraphQL Query Complexity Threshold Exceeded
tickets.description: Customer's dashboard loading extremely slowly due to GraphQL queries exceeding complexity limits. Nested relationship queries timing out after 30 seconds. Need query optimization or limit adjustment.

tickets.title: Redis Cluster Split-Brain Syndrome
tickets.description: Customer's caching layer experiencing split-brain condition causing data inconsistencies. Session data differs between nodes leading to users being randomly logged out or seeing stale information.

tickets.title: Certificate Authority Chain Validation Error
tickets.description: Customer's API clients failing SSL handshake due to incomplete certificate chain. Root CA certificate missing from server configuration. Mobile apps showing 'untrusted certificate' warnings.

tickets.title: Microservice Circuit Breaker False Positives
tickets.description: Customer's order processing system circuit breakers triggering prematurely during normal load. Threshold set at 5% error rate but network latency spikes cause false positives, blocking 40% of valid orders.

tickets.title: MongoDB Replica Set Primary Election Failure
tickets.description: Customer's database cluster unable to elect primary node after maintenance window. All nodes stuck in secondary state causing read-only mode. Application writes failing for 45+ minutes.

tickets.title: Content Security Policy Violation Blocking Assets
tickets.description: Customer's recent CSP implementation blocking legitimate third-party resources including payment processors and analytics. Checkout conversion rate dropped 89% since CSP deployment yesterday.

tickets.title: Apache Kafka Partition Rebalancing Issues
tickets.description: Customer's event streaming pipeline experiencing excessive partition rebalancing causing message processing delays. Consumer groups frequently triggering rebalances affecting real-time data processing.

tickets.title: DNS Propagation Delay for Custom Domain
tickets.description: Customer's custom domain (app.clientdomain.com) showing DNS propagation delays in Asian regions. Users in Japan, Singapore, and Hong Kong unable to access application for 6+ hours.

tickets.title: Load Balancer Health Check False Negatives
tickets.description: Customer's application instances being marked unhealthy despite functioning correctly. Health check endpoint /health returning 200 but load balancer routing traffic to fewer instances causing performance degradation.

tickets.title: RabbitMQ Message Queue Deadlock Condition
tickets.description: Customer's message processing stuck in deadlock condition. Messages accumulating in queue (currently 45,000+ pending) but consumers unable to process due to resource contention on shared database connections.

tickets.title: S3 Cross-Region Replication Lag
tickets.description: Customer's disaster recovery setup experiencing 45+ minute replication lag between us-east-1 and eu-west-1. Recent objects not appearing in backup region within acceptable RTO of 15 minutes.

tickets.title: Docker Registry Pull Rate Limit Exceeded
tickets.description: Customer's CI/CD pipeline failing due to Docker Hub pull rate limits. Build processes timing out during image pull phase. Anonymous pulls exceeded 100/6hrs limit, authenticated pulls at 200/6hrs limit.

tickets.title: ElasticSearch Cluster Yellow State Recovery
tickets.description: Customer's search cluster stuck in yellow state for 72+ hours after node failure. Primary shards healthy but replica shards unallocated. Search performance degraded and no fault tolerance available.

tickets.title: API Gateway Lambda Cold Start Latency
tickets.description: Customer's serverless API experiencing 8-12 second response times due to Lambda cold starts. Functions written in Java with large dependency trees. P99 latency exceeding acceptable 2 second SLA.
